{"tid":2234482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"館長槍擊案｜大逮捕！檢警直搗「竹聯幫寶和會」　兵分18路逮會長林修伯等9人","createTime":"2020-10-08T02:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T05:50:43.000Z","uid":253829,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e91558b02875e04a0b7ded142f3b0080bca68d20","tid":2234482,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T02:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201008/IBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FIBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5CtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=7ca4364f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FIBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA%2F&h=77b0478c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201008/IBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n館長陳之漢今年8月28日凌晨遭到槍擊，槍手劉丞浩隨即跑到派出所投案，但警方懷疑背後有藏鏡人，新北市刑大警方深入追查，發現槍手劉丞浩為竹聯幫寶和會成員，直屬大哥正是46歲的會長林修伯，警方認為林及幫眾與該案有很大的關係，經長達1個月跟監蒐證，昨天（7日）下午持拘票及搜索票，兵分18路帶回林修伯等9名幹部，並強力掃蕩寶和會在北市中山區圍事的酒店。"},{"pid":"91b10a0292d8b5d8c2ef6accf41c64b918bdcb73","tid":2234482,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2d9fd353b4b601bbfc7ddbba6736357142008e","tid":2234482,"uid":126889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"遞解共匪返中国"},{"pid":"bbeb1ce769373981b2793c6fef9b21837c3373c6","tid":2234482,"uid":253829,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20200926/Q3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FQ3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5CtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=225c9d8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FQ3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54%2F&h=f30d1f63\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20200926/Q3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54/</a><br />\n<br />\n「館長」陳之漢上月28日遭男子劉丞浩連開3槍，展現超人恢復力，出院後已開始做重量訓練，昨天還在臉書臥舉150公斤10下。面對酸民頻頻嗆聲，甚至譏「這輩子就廢了」，館長今天也回嗆酸民，「很快的我半年內會深蹲給你看！」"},{"pid":"588a4e50d9feb84ca09b2f7baa477bd29886853e","tid":2234482,"uid":19437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbeb1ce769373981b2793c6fef9b21837c3373c6","tid":2234482,"uid":253829,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20200926/Q3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FQ3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5CtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=225c9d8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FQ3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54%2F&h=f30d1f63\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20200926/Q3P7BWKXGNDBXDG7MZLB2U5Q54/</a><br />\n<br />\n「館長」陳之漢上月28日遭男子劉丞浩連開3槍，展現超人恢復力，出院後已開始做重量訓練，昨天還在臉書臥舉150公斤10下。面對酸民頻頻嗆聲，甚至譏「這輩子就廢了」，館長今天也回嗆酸民，「很快的我半年內會深蹲給你看！」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"傷左都舉得重過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dacef400d3a965feaa025d317f39d56e846abcc","tid":2234482,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e91558b02875e04a0b7ded142f3b0080bca68d20","tid":2234482,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T02:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201008/IBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FIBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5CtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=7ca4364f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FIBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA%2F&h=77b0478c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201008/IBXBITLF7BFODOEHZEVILS3KSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n館長陳之漢今年8月28日凌晨遭到槍擊，槍手劉丞浩隨即跑到派出所投案，但警方懷疑背後有藏鏡人，新北市刑大警方深入追查，發現槍手劉丞浩為竹聯幫寶和會成員，直屬大哥正是46歲的會長林修伯，警方認為林及幫眾與該案有很大的關係，經長達1個月跟監蒐證，昨天（7日）下午持拘票及搜索票，兵分18路帶回林修伯等9名幹部，並強力掃蕩寶和會在北市中山區圍事的酒店。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"白狼果派"},{"pid":"9a7f72bf135d8034c96d43809afa7e559d3c1c6d","tid":2234482,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"型到仆街"},{"pid":"654f27e00d6ee4481e25c745783a60d9048580a1","tid":2234482,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:05:45.000Z","msg":"呢D先係做野..."},{"pid":"9111d18265918fefb80697f1aeffdd8412830c6a","tid":2234482,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"《刃牙》嘅肌肉角色中槍唔死<br />\n原來係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f623d7208792951b9d0c9a11db5a104889c3d6a2","tid":2234482,"uid":253829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"而警方調查更發現，劉嫌住家內沒有電腦等通訊器材，唯一查扣證物就是劉嫌的iPhone手機。但在律師建議下，劉嫌拒絕提供手機密碼，以face ID上鎖的iphone，在沒有密碼的狀況下要打開查看幾乎是不可能的任務，當時傳出警方打算將劉嫌手機送往以色列破解。<br />\n<br />\n不過，如今劉嫌手機順利解鎖，但手機並沒有送出國，而是由國內資安高手破解。據ETtoday新聞雲報導，<span class=\"red\">台灣資安高手出手，短短不到一周時間就順利打開劉男手機</span>，知情警方還說，傳聞要將手機送出國解鎖，也太小看台灣資安實力了。<br />\n<br />\n解鎖後警方發現，劉男犯案前不打電話、不用微信、臉書messenger、LINE，似乎有意避開追查。警方擴大時間範圍，追查到犯案前一周，劉男用「FaceTime」與一名綽號「小J」的人聯絡，追查之下發現「小J」就是竹聯幫寶和會的施俊吉，案情才有所突破。"},{"pid":"525790ad44d3142737ead28d2539e00f23833231","tid":2234482,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"張相雞竇黎?"},{"pid":"e69391b4d7e673cce8c7614b346cbfe5d4b36a66","tid":2234482,"uid":196420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T05:29:28.000Z","ms